'''Rogue Cell Division''' was the branch of the [[Imperial Security Bureau/Legends|Imperial Security Bureau]] that kept watch over all retired [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] and former [[Imperial Military/Legends|Imperial military]] personnel, making sure they did not engage in anti-[[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] activities.

